{"tid":418840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢對你冇愛喇，仲拎自己嘅愛想打動佢？咪傻啦","createTime":"2017-09-30T02:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T04:02:59.000Z","uid":30686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce487bb5dfe7299fc157f0b1fe6e2c542aae9b3","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:32:38.000Z","msg":"過左一個禮拜，雖然心底仲好記掛<br />\n但依加唔係以德報怨嘅時候，佢對我殘忍，仲對佢仁慈真係好on9<br />\n個個都話我只係set左保障男朋友自身安全感同利益嘅限制俾佢<br />\n而佢覺得同異性嘅好朋友出下街夜返好正常<br />\n係呢一刻覺得朋友重要，為左同異性朋友玩得唔洗就住就住，而同我分手<br />\n好啦，你死去你班朋友到啦，俾異性&quot;好朋友&quot;呃蝦條都唔抵可憐呀<br />\n依加你咁窮，又大洗，我就係要拎返啲錢<br />\n仲話啲錢係我講好左我俾返佢，筆數抵銷唔洗俾返我<br />\n咪on9啦，仲同我講&quot;講好左&quot;<br />\n依啲野係輪到你講嘅咩<br />\n你夠講好左會一直一齊落去，一覺得有問題會提出黎解決啦<br />\n依加咪又俾唔撚做，你自私咁解決左<br />\n我好撚心涼<br />\n唔夠俾要俾啲時間你？<br />\n咁你有冇俾啲時間我呀？"},{"pid":"a9e1638d86c2a83f662ae5d9a750ddbf038f4fe7","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"快撚啲還錢呀仆街"},{"pid":"f9003d751a336691e39f2164647c8779c6d2f2b9","tid":418840,"uid":145946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"屌 個標題咁似同我講緊咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f42f4dad2ea0ee8a263b17ccde23b658326be70","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 個標題咁似同我講緊咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗左成個星期得出黎嘅答案<br />\n應該要解脫喇<br />\n人難免有孤單寂寥嘅時候<br />\n如果佢係依個時候諗起你搵返你<br />\n先再去理依一個人<br />\n如果唔係，都係收返埋好啲<br />\n免得損手爛腳"},{"pid":"794d4540b2c6a292002e307c5369379cc6a3915c","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"趕盡殺絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2322ea384999c34928b068cb9a2423eb5c66a0cf","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"喂，還未呀"},{"pid":"aad464ebb8a13d644dc10dc755c5836c525477c8","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"第一次見自己心腸硬"},{"pid":"fdc9800ca5e916c168679147d37f7a1ec8a799b6","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"空間..."},{"pid":"d3ea16f4c9378702adc26dd30d593b7d16a11e4b","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"冇錢用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090a3ad0f876055d92c730ff4a83ef1e220be680","tid":418840,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"快啲答我啦"}]}